./.title: Introduction
./.body:
Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle
Features Overview
Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle provides the interface package for the communication between panel and Tuya Cloud to accelerate the application development process
Supported hardware device type: WIFI 
Unsupported hardware device types: Zigbee、Mesh、BLE
Supported Features：Device panel control and alarm
Unsupported Feature：Groups panel control

resource/Preparation.html.title: Preparation for integration
resource/Preparation.html.body:
Preparation
Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle bases on the Tuya Smart SDK 3.13.0.you can  complete register,create family,configure network by referring to the Tuya Smart SDK Docs ,then you can use the Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle.

resource/PanelDestroy.html.title: Release Panel Resource
resource/PanelDestroy.html.body:
Release the panel resource
Call this method to release resources when exiting the application
Example
TuyaPanel.getInstance().onDestroy();

resource/PanelClear.html.title: Clear Cache
resource/PanelClear.html.body:
Clear all the cache of panel resources
The panel resources files will be stored in the current app storage directory. you can call this method to clean up.
Example
TuyaPanelSDK.getPanelInstance().clearPanelCache();
